description.en: CapCut makes video creation, upload & share easier with frame by frame track editor, cloud drive and cross platform collaboration features on PC & mobile.
description.id: CapCut hadir untuk mempermudahmu mengedit video, mengunggah & berbagi lebih mudah dengan editor trek bingkai demi bingkai, drive cloud, dan fitur kolaborasi antar platform di PC & seluler.
